pr_title: Add data generation code and Update lodbrok
pr_body:
- Added dummy data generation code with relevant doc files in the data folder.
- Trained and evaluated lodbrok with the latest dummy data, documented the same with results.
- Organized the files in proper folders and deleted unnecessary files.

pr_title: Add retrain code with all the dependencies
pr_body:
- Created retrain_dataset_generation notebook for test, eval, predict dataset to retrain the model.
- Created retrain_model function with a static learning rate.
- Updated preprocessing.py to preprocess data outside the dataset_generation notebook.
